	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Colendissime domine <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingere</persName>, quod nunc scribam, nil habeo praeter quod relatum est regis <persName type="auto_name">Philippi</persName> classem a <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510">Turca</placeName> prope <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1374">Tripolim</placeName> superatam esse et proinde triremes vel onerarias naves circiter 60 amisisse.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Et sane dolendum, quod rex christianus tantam iacturam accepit ab hoste nominis christiani maximo.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Caeterum hic sumus satis quieti, nisi quod perpetuo adhuc acri penuria molestamur; speramus tamen eam aliquando remissum iri, idque faciat deus.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">- Ego cum meis omnibus bene valeo dei beneficio; id ipsum vero enixe abs te tuisque audire cupio, quos optimus deus iugiter servet incolumes.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Opinor me nundinas <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l98" cert="high">Churienses</placeName> nunc instantes accessurum tuncque latius <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l98" cert="high">Churia</placeName> sum tibi scripturus et maxime, si quid novi ingruerit.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Filius meus iubet te cum omnibus domesticis admodum valere vosque omnes salutat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale multum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Datum raptim <placeName ref="l93" cert="high">Clavennae</placeName> 2. iunii 1560.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tibi omnium deditissimus <persName ref="p8432" cert="high">Federicus a Salice</persName>, commissarius <placeName ref="l93" cert="high">Clavennę</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ornatissimo et clarissimo viro domino <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Henrico Bullingero</persName>, domino meo iugiter colendissimo.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName> Helvetiorum.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
